By Yinka Adeniran, Ibadan  The massive structure housing illegal detainees at Ojoo axis of Ibadan, the Oyo state capital has been ordered for demolition by Governor Seyi Makinde. The Governor made the pronouncement during a visit to the Olaoore Central Mosque, Ojoo where over 200 detainees were released on Monday. He is also leading a team of top government functionaries to the camp where the freed victims are being rehabilitated by the government Details shortlyâ€¦.